data.description: Welcome to Your Lakefront Front Dream Home with a pool in Anthony Groves! This stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom oasis boasts luxury living at its finest. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautifully laid tile, upgraded baseboards, and crown molding throughout the main living area. The open concept kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring solid cabinetry, stainless steel LG appliances with a gas stove, granite countertops, a large center island, and a dedicated pantry. With LED recessed lighting and upgraded crown molding, this kitchen is as stylish as it is functional. Entertain in style in the spacious family room, complete with upgraded baseboards, crown molding, and sliding glass doors leading out to the backyard pool area. The oversized formal living room offers additional space for gatherings, with upgraded features including crown molding and LED recessed lighting. Upstairs, you'll find five generously sized bedrooms, each boasting upgraded fans, ample closet space, and upgraded window treatments. The master suite is a retreat in itself, featuring a tray ceiling, walk-in closet with custom organizers, and a luxurious master bathroom with his and hers vanities, a walk-in shower, and a separate soaking tub. Step outside to your own private paradise, with a freeform swimming pool, paver patio deck, custom outdoor BBQ area, and breathtaking lake views. Additional upgrades include a new upstairs AC (2021) and hot water heater (2018). Enjoy the amenities of the Anthony Groves community, including a clubhouse, resort-style pool, fitness center, tennis/pickleball courts, hockey rink, soccer field, picnic area, and playground. Monthly HOA includes internet, lawn care, basic cable, and manned gate. With A-rated schools nearby and easy access to shopping, dining, and major highways, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and luxury living.
